'''Álex Adrián Arce Barrios''' (born 16 June 1995) is a Paraguayan professional [[Association football|footballer]] who plays as a [[Forward (association football)|striker]] for Argentine club [[Independiente Rivadavia]] and the [[Paraguay national football team|Paraguay national team]].

==Early life==
Arce came through the youth academy at Cerro Porteño and signed his first contract in 2015. However, he had to wait almost two years to make his debut in the top category and shortly afterwards suffered a cruciate ligament rupture. After recovering, his level was not the same and that is why he spent a lot of time training with the team's Reserve, until in 2019 he decided to leave to seek continuity in a minor league club.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.infobae.com/deportes/2023/06/28/de-vendedor-ambulante-en-paraguay-a-ser-el-maximo-goleador-del-futbol-argentino-la-historia-de-superacion-de-alex-arce/|title=De vendedor ambulante en Paraguay a ser el máximo goleador del fútbol argentino: la historia de superación de Álex Arce|date=28 June 2023 |publisher=infobae.com}}</ref>

==Club career==
Arce played for Paraguayan side [[Sportivo Ameliano]], helping the club achieve promotion.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.cronica.com.ar/depo/ascenso/Alex-Arce-el-Erling-Haaland-que-tiene-Independiente-Rivadavia-y-todo-el-futbol-argentino-20230623-0035.html|title=Álex Arce, el Erling Haaland que tiene Independiente Rivadavia y todo el fútbol argentino|publisher=cronica.com.py}}</ref>

==International career==
Arce made his debut for the [[Paraguay national football team|Paraguay national team]] on 7 June 2024 in a friendly against [[Peru national football team|Peru]] at [[Estadio Monumental "U"|Estadio Monumental]]. He started the game and played 65 minutes in a 0–0 draw.<ref>{{cite web|publisher=ESPN|url=https://www.espn.com/soccer/match/_/gameId/701635|title=Peru v Paraguay game report|date=7 June 2024}}</ref>

==Style of play==
Arce mainly operates as a striker and has been described as "stands out for kicking from outside the area with both legs , executing free kicks, dribbling at speed and As if that were not enough, his 187 centimeters and strength in jumping made him add a dangerous aerial game".<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.tycsports.com/al-angulo/alex-arce-independiente-rivadavia-jugaba-en-una-liga-amateur-historia-id522506.html|title=Jugaba en una liga amateur, fue vendedor ambulante y es el goleador del fútbol argentino: la historia de Álex Arce|date=12 July 2023 |publisher=tycsports.com}}</ref>

==Personal life==
Arce is the son of Miriam Barrios.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.cronica.com.py/2021/08/06/alex-arce-quiero-ser-goleador-en-la-primera/|title=ÁLEX ARCE: "QUIERO SER GOLEADOR EN LA PRIMERA"|publisher=cronica.com.py|date=2021-08-06|last=Rojas C.|first=Arturo}}</ref>

